 <text>
  <front>
   <head>On the Same.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">was just slipt into Bed:</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Her Eye-brows on the Toilet lay:</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Away the Kitten with them fled,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">As Fees belonging to her Prey.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">For this Misfortune careless ,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Assure your self, was loudly rated:</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And Madam getting up again,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">With her own Hand the Mouse-Trap baited.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">On little Things, as Sages write,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Depends our Human Joy, or Sorrow:</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">If We don't catch a Mouse To-night,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Alas! no Eye-brows for To-morrow.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
